title: #186 - We Speak With An Epidemiologist About Coronavirus
description: Newest episode of the podcast is up! This one is a little different- we spoke via Zoom to Dr. Eric Ding, an epidemiologist we've mentioned on the show before about where we are with Coronavirus and what we can do it beat this thing! Stay safe everyone!
